teacher milton evertz leaned down and spoke 
inches from his pupil marias ear listen to me say it just as 
im saying it west west west west 
wet wet wet she replied finding the letter s a 
challenge for her hispanic tongue 
you mean like mojado asked evertz laughing heartily 
