frontier that divides mongolia and china however the soviet union 
last year began withdrawing its troops and says the last of 60000 
soviet soldiers will leave mongolia by 1992 
mongolia which has a population of only 2 million in a nation 
nearly as big as all of west europe became the worlds second 
communist state in 1921 
china which in the past laid claims to all of mongolia did not 
recognize the sovietallied state until the chinese communists came 
to power in 1949 
