down from 354 billion from the yearago period combined revenues 
fell 11 percent to 6127 billion 
gm said it earned 710 million or 102 per share of common 
stock on revenues of 3011 billion compared with 155 billion 
or 237 a share on revenues of 3324 billion in the yearago 
period 
