that his country would cut its oil production to 19 million 
barrels a day from 21 million barrels 
the statement caused industry analysts to doubt the persian gulf 
countrys commitment to lowering output because they estimate the 
uaes actual production already is at 19 million barrels 
at best analysts predicted the cartel will muster a total 
reduction of 1 million barrels 
